let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    	match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        	    Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      	  | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    	match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        	    Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      	  | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    	match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        	    Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      	  | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) =

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    	match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        	    Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      	  | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    	match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        	    Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      	  | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) =

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");

  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException

  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in

    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"

let _ = runAllTests ()

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");

  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

  let testBad x = 0 in

let padZero l1 l2 = 
  let numZeros = List.length l1 - List.length l2 in
    if numZeros = 0 then [l1, l2]
    else 
      let listZeros = clone(0, abs(numZeros)) in
        if numZeros > 0 then 
          let list1 = l1 in
          let list2 = listZeros@l2 in 
            [list1, list2]
        else let list1 = listZeros@l1 in 
          let list2 = l2 in 
            [list1, list2]

let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException

  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in

    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&

    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in

      | Fail -> "[fail]"

    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let prefix130 = "130" (*XXXXXXXX*)
let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s =

    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");

     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

res (* answer is in res *)

let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let add (l1, l2) = 
let f a x =  

let (carry, currentSum) = a in 
if x = [] then (0, carry::currentSum)
else 
let (toSum1, toSum2) = x in
(* f returns tuple and f recurses on itself  *)
let intermediateValue = toSum1 + toSum2 + carry in
let valueToAddToArray = intermediateValue mod 10 in
let carry = intermediateValue / 10 in
(carry, valueToAddToArray::currentSum) in

(* returns tuple (a, b) where b is a list of ints
* want to accumulate the answer in b 
* takes in what exists so far in a, b is the new piece 
* that you want to incorporate into the sum

* 
*)
let base = (0, []) in
let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
let (_, res) = List.fold_left f base args in
res (* answer is in res *)

removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2))

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in

     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in

    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let _ = print130 ("Compiled"^key^"\n")

let bigAdd l1 l2 = 
let add (l1, l2) = 
let f a x =  

let (carry, currentCarry::currentSum) = a in 
let (toSum1, toSum2) = x in
(* f returns tuple and f recurses on itself  *)
let intermediateValue = toSum1 + toSum2 + currentCarry in
let valueToAddToArray = intermediateValue mod 10 in
let carry = intermediateValue / 10 in
(carry, carry::valueToAddToArray::currentSum) in

(* returns tuple (a, b) where b is a list of ints
* want to accumulate the answer in b 
* takes in what exists so far in a, b is the new piece 
* that you want to incorporate into the sum
* want to add each piece to the front.
* add the pair together, mod by 10, put that number into the front
* of the accumulated array, and then get the carry?
* have the head of a be the carry? 
* 
*)
let base = (0, [0]) in
let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
let (_, res) = List.fold_left f base args in
res (* answer is in res *)
in 
removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2))

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");

     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in

    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let key = "" (*XXXXXXXX*)

let print130 s = print_string (prefix130^">>"^s)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

(*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("---",[]), "", 1, "sepConcat 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("",["a";"b";"c";"d";"e"]), "abcde", 1, "sepConcat 3");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, ("X",["hello"]), "hello", 1, "sepConcat 4");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, (string_of_int,[1;2;3;4;5;6]), "[1; 2; 3; 4; 5; 6]",1,"stringOfList 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((fun x -> x),["foo"]), "[foo]",1,"stringOfList 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 stringOfList, ((stringOfList string_of_int),[[1;2;3];[4;5];[6];[]]), "[[1; 2; 3]; [4; 5]; [6]; []]",1,"stringOfList 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (3,5), [3;3;3;3;3],1,"clone 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, ("foo",2), ["foo";"foo"],1,"clone 2");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 clone, (clone,-3), [],1,"clone 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), ([0;0;9;9],[1;0;0;2]),1,"padzero 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 padZero, ([1;0;0;2],[9;9]), ([1;0;0;2],[0;0;9;9]),1,"padzero 2");

     runTest(removeZero, [0;0;0;1;0;0;2], [1;0;0;2],1,"removeZero 1");
     runTest(removeZero, [9;9], [9;9],1,"removeZero 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in
  let _ = List.iter print130 (report@([s])) in
    (!score,!max)

let _ = runAllTests ()

let padZero l1 l2 = 
  let numZeros = List.length l1 - List.length l2 in
  let absNumZeros = abs numZeros in 
    if numZeros = 0 then (l1, l2) 
    else let listZeros = clone 0 absNumZeros in 
        if numZeros > 0 then (l1, listZeros@l2) else (listZeros@l1, l2)

exception ErrorCode of string

type result = Pass | Fail | ErrorCode of string

let score = ref 0
let max = ref 0
let timeout = 300

let runWTimeout (f,arg,out,time) = 
  try if compare (f arg) out = 0 then Pass else Fail
  with e -> (print130 ("Uncaught Exception: "^(Printexc.to_string e)^"\n"); ErrorCode "exception") 

exception TestException
let testTest () =
  let testGood x = 1 in
  let testBad x = 0 in 
  let testException x = raise TestException in
  let rec testTimeout x = testTimeout x in
    runWTimeout(testGood,0,1,5) = Pass &&  
    runWTimeout(testBad,0,1,5) = Fail &&  
    runWTimeout(testException,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "exception" && 
    runWTimeout(testTimeout,0,1,5) = ErrorCode "timeout"


let runTest (f,arg,out,points,name) =
  let _ = max := !max + points in
  let outs = 
    match runWTimeout(f,arg,out,timeout) with 
        Pass -> (score := !score + points; "[pass]")
      | Fail -> "[fail]"
      | ErrorCode e -> "[error: "^e^"]"  in
    name^" "^outs^" ("^(string_of_int points)^")\n"

let explode s = 
  let rec _exp i = 
    if i >= String.length s then [] else (s.[i])::(_exp (i+1)) in
    _exp 0

let implode cs = 
  String.concat "" (List.map (String.make 1) cs)

let drop_paren s = 
  implode (List.filter (fun c -> not (List.mem c ['(';' ';')'])) (explode s))

let eq_real p (r1,r2) = 
  (r1 -. r2) < p || (r2 -. r1) < p

let wrap_curried_2 f (a,b) = f a b

let runAllTests () =
  let _ = (score := 0; max := 0) in
  let report = 
    [runTest (sqsum, [], 0, 1, "sqsum 1");
     runTest (sqsum, [1;2;3;4], 30, 1, "sqsum 2");
     runTest (sqsum, [-1;-2;-3;-4], 30, 1, "sqsum 3");

     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([], 3), 3, 1, "pipe 1");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x-> 2*x);(fun x -> x + 3)], 3), 9, 1, "pipe 2");
     runTest (wrap_curried_2 pipe, ([(fun x -> x + 3); (fun x-> 2*x)], 3), 12, 1, "pipe 3");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 sepConcat, (", ",["foo";"bar";"baz"]), "foo, bar, baz", 1, "sepConcat 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9],[1;0;0;2]), [1;1;0;1],1, "bigAdd 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigAdd,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9]), [1;0;9;9;8],1, "bigAdd 2");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 mulByDigit,  (9,[9;9;9;9]), [8;9;9;9;1],1, "mulByDigit 1");

     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;8;0;0;0;1],1, "bigMul 1");
     runTest(wrap_curried_2 bigMul,  ([9;9;9;9;9],[9;9;9;9;9]), [9;9;9;9;8;0;0;0;0;1],1,"bigMul 2");
    ] in
  let s = Format.sprintf "Results: Score/Max = %d / %d \n" !score !max in

let _ = runAllTests ()

let padZero l1 l2 = 
  let numZeros = List.length l1 - List.length l2 in
  let absNumZeros = abs numZeros in 
    if numZeros = 0 then (l1, l2) 
    else let listZeros = clone 0 absNumZeros in 
        if numZeros > 0 then (l1, listZeros@l2) else (listZeros@l1, l2)

  | 0::t -> removeZero t
  | h::t -> l

let bigAdd l1 l2 = 
  let add (l1, l2) = 
    let f a x =  

      let (_, currentCarry::currentSum) = a in 
      let (toSum1, toSum2) = x in
      (*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
      let intermediateValue = toSum1 + toSum2 + currentCarry in
      let valueToAddToArray = intermediateValue mod 10 in
      let carry = intermediateValue / 10 in
        (carry, carry::valueToAddToArray::currentSum) in
    (*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX
XXXXXXX
XXXX*)
    let base = (0, [0]) in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_, res) = List.fold_left f base args in
      res (*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
  in 
    removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2))

let bigAdd l1 l2 = 
  let add (l1, l2) = 
    let f a x =  

      let (_, currentCarry::currentSum)= a in 
      let (toSum1, toSum2) = x in
      (*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
      let intermediateValue = toSum1 + toSum2 + currentCarry in
      let valueToAddToArray = intermediateValue mod 10 in
      let carry = intermediateValue / 10 in
        (carry, carry::valueToAddToArray::currentSum) in
    (*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX

XXXX*)
    let base = (0, [0]) in
    let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
    let (_, res) = List.fold_left f base args in
      res (*XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX*)
  in 
    removeZero (add (padZero l1 l2))

let bigMul l1 l2 = 
  let f a x = 
    let (padCount, currList) = a in
    let intermediateSum = mulByDigit x l2 in
    let rec generatePadding numZeros = 
      if numZeros <= 0 then []
      else 0::generatePadding (numZeros - 1) in
    let toSum = intermediateSum@(generatePadding padCount) in 
      (padCount + 1, bigAdd currList toSum) in 
  let base = (0, []) in
  let args = l1 in 
  let (_, res) = List.fold_left f base args in
    res

*)

let args = List.rev (List.combine l1 l2) in
let (_, res) = List.fold_left f base args in
res (* answer is in res *)
in

        if numZeros > 0 then (l1, listZeros@l2) else (listZeros@l1, l2)
